<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <title></title>
        <style>
            h1{color: #0094ff;
              background-color:indigo; (背景顏色)
               box-shadow:3px 3px 4px rgba;
               text-transform: uppercase}
            h2{text-transform: lowercase}
            h3{text-transform: capitalize}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>這是範例This is example font.</h1>
        <h2>這是範例This is example font.</h2>
        <h3>這是範例This is example font.</h3>
    </body>
   box-shadow - 產生陰影效果或光暈效果的特性
   text-transform:uppercase  -字母均為大寫
   text-transform:lowercase  -字母均為小寫
   text-transform:capitalize -第一個字母是大寫，其餘為小寫
</html>
